  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                  Plot Outline
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
        
   A team of the toughest construction workers in the world has taken on the 
   building of the biggest concrete arch bridge in North America, right next 
   to the famous Hoover Dam; blasting huge foundations out of sheer rock 
   cliffs in the scorching desert heat.
  
